Project Bong Wallpaper Plus Description
Bong Wallpaper Plus downloads the latest bing wallpaper automatically at startup. The wallpaper is then displayed on your desktop.

Bong Wallpaper Plus features
- Annotation of wallpapers
- Runs on workplace computers without admin privileges
- Installs on workplace computers without admin privileges
- Runs at startup
- Can download through proxies
- Minimum invasive code
- Beautiful desktop wallpaper
